                        <interp inst="t18560204-270-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp>There were two other indictments against the prisoner for embezzlement,</rs> 
                     <rs id="t18560204-270-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18560204-270-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
